  <h1>
      Helping Manufacturers Representatives...
  </h1>
  
  <h3>
  RSVP-SIS helps Manufacturers Representatives: 
  </h3>
  <ul>
    <li>By providing local engineering services that understand their technology</li>
    <li>Creating custom solutions using their Manufacturers components and solutions</li>
    <li>Providing an alternative marketing channel</li>
    <li>With new product introductions and launch campaigns</li>
    <li>With local and internet based trainings, tutorials, and workshops</li>
    <li>We can harness social networking to better expand your reach</li>
  </ul>
  <p>
    How many times have you been handed a reference or demo design from one of your manufacturers, that uses <i>Key</i> components that direcly compete with your other/main lines? It's really hard to take that out to your clients, isn't it? Well, we're here to help &endash; we can help to support and defend ALL of your lines; so you can demonstrate your value to your principals.
  </p>
  
  <p>
    Contact us to see how we are helping Manufacturers Representatives. 
  </p>

